    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed. Achieved levels are below required levels across multiple factors; however, compensating controls and conservative safety margins on the clinical hemolysis threshold provide sufficient confidence for submission. Assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU with documented gaps noted for post-market surveillance.",
